    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to let this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in incredible shape\u2014it genuinely looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, always kept in the garage, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership stress, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
