      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely gorgeous, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the lot! It drives like an absolute dream and the interior is still pristine. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it!",
