    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce 333 hp. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, benefiting from fresh bushings and a perfectly calibrated suspension. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with no stone chips or swirl marks, while the interior leather and trim show zero signs of wear or UV damage. A mechanically pure, turn-key investment for the serious driver.",
